---
import Layout from '../../layouts/index.astro'
---

<Layout title='Nuestra Historia de Amor | Amy' description='Una línea de tiempo de nuestro amor'>
  <section class='timeline-container'>
    <header class='header'>
      <h1>Nuestra Historia de Amor</h1>
      <p>3 años y 5 meses juntos 💖</p>
      <div class='heart'>💖</div>
    </header>

    <div class='timeline'>
      <div class='timeline-line'></div>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='41'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776886369/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/abril-12-2026_i6sui1.jpg'
              alt='Ahora'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>41 meses - Abril 2026</span>
            <h3>3 Años y 5 Meses 💍</h3>
            <p>Cada día te amo más. Eres mi futuro, mi todo. Pronto seremos marido y mujer 💑</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='36'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776886368/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/nv-12-2025_beycpz.jpg'
              alt='3 años'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>36 meses - Noviembre 2025</span>
            <h3>3 Años Juntos 💖</h3>
            <p>Tres años de acompañarte. Eres lo mejor de mi vida. Te amo infinitamente ❤️</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='30'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776886373/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/may-12-2025_kw83yk.jpg'
              alt='30 meses'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>30 meses - Mayo 2025</span>
            <h3>2 Años y 6 Meses 😍</h3>
            <p>Mitad del tercer año. Gracias por tanto amor y apoyo. Eres mi compañera de vida 💕</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='24'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776885779/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/nov-12-2024_zhwsyf.webp'
              alt='2 años'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>24 meses - Noviembre 2024</span>
            <h3>2 Años de Amor 💑</h3>
            <p>Dos belleaños juntos. Has sido mi mayor bendición. Te amo más que nunca 💖</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='18'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776885780/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/may-12-2024_k5h28p.jpg'
              alt='18 meses'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>18 meses - Mayo 2024</span>
            <h3>Un Año y Medio 💕</h3>
            <p>Un año y medio de felicidad. Gracias por tanto amor. Eres mi todo ❤️</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='12'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776885782/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/nov-12-2023_rqhpwt.jpg'
              alt='1 año'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>12 meses - Noviembre 2023</span>
            <h3>Nuestro Primer Año 💍</h3>
            <p>El inicio de todo. Un año lleno de mucho amor y felicidad, agradeciéndote por cada momento juntos. 💑</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class='timeline-item' data-month='3'>
        <div class='timeline-dot'></div>
        <div class='timeline-content'>
          <div class='photo-container'>
            <img
              src='https://res.cloudinary.com/john-serrano/image/upload/v1776886049/John%20Serrano/Andrey%20-%20Ammi/12-marzo-2023_gs2lg4.webp'
              alt='Mes 3'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='message'>
            <span class='month'>Mes 3 - Marzo 2023</span>
            <h3>Tres Meses de Amor 💖</h3>
            <p>
              3 meses de pura felicidad. Gracias por tu amor y tiempo. Eres mi sueño hecho realidad. Te amo con toda mi
              alma y corazón.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
    <footer class='footer-timeline'>
      <div class='hearts'>💖 💖 💖</div>
      <p>Te amo mi reina, mi ya casi esposa 💍</p>
      <p class='signature'>Andrey Serrano ❤</p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .timeline-container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #2d1015 50%, #1a0a0a 100%);
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .timeline-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #f8bbd0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.5);
    animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes glow {
    from {
      text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.5);
    }
    to {
      text-shadow:
        0 0 40px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.8),
        0 0 60px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.4);
    }
  }

  .header p {
    color: #f48fb1;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .heart {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    animation: heartbeat 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes heartbeat {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.15);
    }
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 3px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e91e63 0%, #f48fb1 50%, #e91e63 100%);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    min-height: 140px;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 0.4s;
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(5) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(6) {
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: #e91e63;
    border: 3px solid #f8bbd0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 2;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.6);
    top: 50%;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 42%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03);
    border-color: rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.3);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .photo-container {
    width: 80px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 2px solid rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.4);
  }

  .photo-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover .photo-container img {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .message {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .month {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #f48fb1;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .message h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #f8bbd0;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .message p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.4;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .footer-timeline {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hearts {
    font-size: 2rem;
    animation: heartbeat 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .footer-timeline p {
    color: #f48fb1;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .signature {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f8bbd0 !important;
    font-size: 1.3rem !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .timeline-line {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-dot {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      width: calc(100% - 50px);
      margin-left: 50px;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .timeline-container {
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .photo-container {
      width: 100%;
      height: 390px;
    }

    .message p {
      -webkit-line-clamp: 4;
    }
  }
</style>
